import React from "react"
import { Container, Nav, Navbar, NavDropdown, Form, FormControl, Button } from 'react-bootstrap';


function NavBar() {
    return (
        <Navbar bg="none" expand="lg">
            <Navbar.Brand href="#home">Shortly</Navbar.Brand>
            <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
            <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">

                <Nav className="mr-auto">
                    <Nav.Link href="#home" id="feature" ClassName="nav-item-left">Feature</Nav.Link>
                    <Nav.Link href="#link" id="pricing" ClassName="nav-item-left">Pricing</Nav.Link>
                    <Nav.Link href="#link" id="resources" ClassName="nav-item-left">Resources</Nav.Link>

                </Nav>
                <Nav>
                    <Nav.Link href="#link" id="login" ClassName="nav-item-right">Login</Nav.Link>
                    <Nav.Link href="#link" id="sign-up" ClassName="nav-item-right">Sign Up</Nav.Link>
                </Nav>
            </Navbar.Collapse>
        </Navbar>
    )
}

export default NavBar;
